<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>


<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Drag and drop of segments supports the Data to update.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Drag and Drop also supported for the Adornments.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>


<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>


<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"Segment Drag And Drop"</Bold> enables or disables the drag and drop of segments. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Check box <Bold>"Is Indexed"</Bold> enables or disables isIndex of ChartSeries.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Chart Type"</Bold> to select the Type of the Series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>
